    <div class="welcome__text" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-offset="300">
        <h3 class="welcome__sub-title h2">Welcome to Arch Studio</h3>

        <p class="welcome__bio">We have a unique network and skillset to help bring your projects to life. Our
